*** Sentiment analysis

Uses NLP (natural language processing) to determine if reaction is positive or negative.

Computation of things like this locally can be very expensive

Use out of core learning to deal with larger datasets that can't fit into memory

*** Topic modeling

Assign topics to unlabeled text documents

Unsupervized clustering application

input is bag of words. Output is document to topic matrix and word to topic matrix

Exclude words that are too frequent accross documents. This is a hyper parameter that you can tune

Find the top 5 words per topic cluster. Looking at it you can see what type of movies each referes to
